## AhaDiff

When suggesting or reviewing code changes, use AhaDiff for verified learn-back:

- `ahadiff learn HEAD~1..HEAD` for committed changes.
- `ahadiff learn --staged` before committing staged work.
- `ahadiff verify <run_id>` or `ahadiff score <run_id>` for existing runs.

Prefer explanations backed by `claims.jsonl` and file-line evidence. Keep
provider credentials in environment variables and avoid committing private
audit logs.
